definitions.definition: A dog trained in pursuit of game in the field.
( baseball , softball ) A defensive player in the field .

main_definition: A dog trained in pursuit of game in the field.
secondary_definitions: ( baseball , softball ) A defensive player in the field .

definitions.definition: Agent noun of field : one who fields anything.
A player of the fielding side, whose task is to gather the ball after the batsman has hit it, to catch the batsman out, or to prevent him from scoring.
examples: His best fielder took the big wicket of the opponent team.
